Webconverger uses the serif [Gentium font](http://scripts.sil.org/Gentium), which is included on every Webconverger distribution since version 2.21.


# Installing on a Debian/Ubuntu machine

  1. `monty:~% sudo apt-get install ttf-gentium`
  2. Restart your browser

